{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"SGML","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/SGML","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>標準通用標記式語言（Standard Generalized Markup Language 或簡稱 &nbsp;<strong>SGML</strong>）是一套 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/ISO\">ISO <small>(en-US)</small></a> 所定義，用來規範宣告式標記語言的標準。</p>\n<p>在 Web 環境當中，<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/HTML\">HTML</a> 4、<a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/XHTML\">XHTML</a> 以及 &nbsp;<a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/XML\">XML <small>(en-US)</small></a> 都是知名的以 SGML 為基礎的語言。然而值得一提的是，HTML 自第五版起擁有了自己的剖析規則，不再是以 &nbsp;SGML 為基礎的語言。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"了解更多","title":"了解更多","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>維基百科上的 <a title=\"SGML\" href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/SGML\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">SGML</a> 條目</li>\n  <li><a href=\"http://www.isgmlug.org/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">SGML 簡介</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"了解更多","id":"了解更多"}],"summary":"標準通用標記式語言（Standard Generalized Markup Language 或簡稱  SGML）是一套 ISO (en-US) 所定義，用來規範宣告式標記語言的標準。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"SGML","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"SGML","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"SGML","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"SGML","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"SGML","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"SGML","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"SGML","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/glossary/sgml","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-tw/glossary/sgml/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab419